            <updated>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 11:29:05 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p>贝特恩（BTNature）蓝胖子牛奶粉 1kg 日常售价 89 元，今日天猫国际直降至 55.63 元。</p><p>本次需击宝贝详情页<span class="font-color-red"><strong>“淘宝秒杀限时疯抢”红色横幅</strong></span>下单哦：</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?e=evmlOl84JjRdoqAawkp85SAd78rJKA5EEHGbjhgs%2FwmMFiFW%2FRDw4kEtBZbv320qB87BulwV17jy3U3gEJTxCLEP%2Fx2YMJHApRwaHAguF7cPCswtfh8YwvNYkAlh5KvOT2%2FUpkVf5qDabAJjl9LutWtN1PtyBd%2FqOBhJinGZi0yxv6%2BLvWntiGVfKa%2BhVnND3EOO%2FFaFqnv5gee3CZoaAZjB6TX2HR3Q1BXe0Gl0oeh3EmBGYfo9NQ%2BtFP8aV69JTOAoiTpdOyWKo%2FrC95AUFasE1FTK%2FEs4FMk3EuQjF4gbLLRiEexPNOjUJIoGvi1Fzt9rsOOJVw6HLHsZXt2tvn44d%2BzmctAY&amp;traceId=215045f917747814128523049e1602&amp;&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1774781412@2104fe53_171a_19d3937362d_7e4f@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i4/2549841410/O1CN01jNVCzD1MHpX42FVmn_!!2549841410-0-tmg_sticker_daily.jpg" title="3.6g 蛋白质 +113mg 高钙：澳洲贝特恩蓝胖子奶粉 2 斤 55.8 元商超大差价" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">贝特恩蓝一号牛奶粉 1kg</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> 澳洲进口</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">秒杀 55.63 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 10 元券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>宝贝详情页“淘宝秒杀限时疯抢”红色横幅：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="306" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/3/902e069a-12f0-4776-a320-1d939e6c761e.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="3.6g 蛋白质 +113mg 高钙：澳洲贝特恩蓝胖子奶粉 2 斤 55.8 元商超大差价" width="883" /></p><p>京东自营百亿补贴仍需 78 元，30 多元大差价：<a href="https://lapin.ithome.com/html/digi/null" target="_blank">点此查看</a>。</p><h3><strong>此款为贝特恩，非美可卓。</strong></h3><p>每 35g 可冲泡 250ml，冲泡后 3.6g 蛋白质 / 100ml，<strong>113mg 钙 / 100ml（约 8 倍鲜奶含量）</strong>。</p><p>另外以 250ml / 杯为准，1kg 奶粉可冲泡 28.5 杯，<strong>单杯仅需 1.95 元</strong>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="854" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfi